This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the cyberagent organization:
- cyberagent/open-calm-1b tokenizer.json
- cyberagent/calm2-7b tokenizer.json
- cyberagent/calm3-22b-chat tokenizer.json

The following supported model names are aliases confirmed to reuse those bundled tokenizer assets and are not shipped as separate snapshots:
- cyberagent/open-calm-small
- cyberagent/open-calm-medium
- cyberagent/open-calm-3b
- cyberagent/open-calm-large
- cyberagent/open-calm-7b
- cyberagent/calm2-7b-chat

This package distributes tokenizer assets under a mixed-license layout:
- cyberagent/open-calm-1b tokenizer.json: CC-BY-SA-4.0
- cyberagent/calm2-7b tokenizer.json: Apache-2.0
- cyberagent/calm3-22b-chat tokenizer.json: Apache-2.0

